[SPEAKER_00]: We'll all take another crack at any comments that we have, and then we can send that off, and hopefully we can get some comments back from Commissioner Fordy as well.

1019
01:47:19,864 --> 01:47:20,105
[SPEAKER_00]: Great.

1020
01:47:20,165 --> 01:47:20,645
[SPEAKER_00]: You second it?

1021
01:47:20,785 --> 01:47:21,605
[SPEAKER_00]: Yeah, I'll second that motion.

1022
01:47:25,325 --> 01:47:30,711
[SPEAKER_00]: Before we vote on the motions, just any further comments or discussion from anyone on the process going forward?

1023
01:47:30,731 --> 01:47:32,794
[SPEAKER_00]: Does that sound like the right process to take?

1024
01:47:34,936 --> 01:47:36,258
[SPEAKER_00]: Great, got nods on it.

1025
01:47:36,278 --> 01:47:38,901
[SPEAKER_00]: So yeah, if Mr. Clerk, will you please call the roll?

1026
