[SPEAKER_00]: Or you don't have to, just...

1027
01:47:42,365 --> 01:47:58,777
[SPEAKER_05]: On the motion of Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council Council

1028
01:48:02,740 --> 01:48:06,345
[SPEAKER_05]: To subcommittee members, the department heads here tonight and legal counsel for comment.

1029
01:48:06,926 --> 01:48:07,526
[SPEAKER_05]: Second from you.

1030
01:48:07,627 --> 01:48:07,867
[SPEAKER_00]: Great.

1031
01:48:07,947 --> 01:48:08,628
[SPEAKER_00]: All those in favor?

1032
01:48:08,648 --> 01:48:09,209
[SPEAKER_00]: Aye.

1033
01:48:09,529 --> 01:48:10,330
[SPEAKER_00]: Motion passes.

1034
01:48:11,051 --> 01:48:13,934
[SPEAKER_00]: Any further discussion before we conclude?

1035
01:48:15,737 --> 01:48:17,679
[SPEAKER_00]: Seeing none, is there a motion to adjourn?

1036
01:48:17,699 --> 01:48:19,101
[SPEAKER_07]: Motion to adjourn.

1037
01:48:19,328 --> 01:48:22,411
